Resource Profile: CH ELM Composition: Laboratory Report

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-elm/StructureDefinition/ch-elm-composition Version: 1.9.1
Active as of 2025-03-26 Computable Name: ChElmComposition

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This CH ELM base profile constrains the Composition resource for the purpose of laboratory test reports.

  • Derived from this Resource Profile: CH ELM Composition: Laboratory Report Strict
